{"id":307946,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-山东陈志强家深夜遭遇强拆，家人遭殴打/","date":"2013-08-08T00:48:22Z","modified":"2013-08-08T00:48:22Z","title":"维权网 | 山东陈志强家深夜遭遇强拆，家人遭殴打致重伤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李娜报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日，位于山东省济南市槐荫区段店镇大金办事处的演马村，村民陈志强家合法院落在凌晨一点左右，遭到一伙不明身份的暴徒袭击。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据受害人陈志强说：一群暴徒于凌晨一时左右，手持镐把强行破门，并持催泪瓦斯，先向室内喷洒，再撬坏房门，正在熟睡的陈志强一家五口连鞋都来不及穿即遭绑架，随后，一伙暴徒殴打陈志强的家人，致使两人身受重伤，后送院治疗方脱离生命危险。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈志强一家人被释放回到自己的合法住宅后，只见两层楼房已经被夷为平地，所有家具包括电脑、电视机以及孩子学摄影用的高级照相机等器材，连身上穿的衣物都没带出一件，尽被掩埋在废墟之下。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>案发当时他们拨打</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110 </span><span>后，原本步行仅需五分钟的路程，有半个多小时警察才到，警察到现场后扣留了违法车辆，拘留了一名肇事司机，两个车主，后车主取保。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>报案后没有出具刑事案件受理回执单，据警察对陈志强说，立案后司机已经说了绑架和故意毁坏的犯罪嫌疑人，但嫌疑人已经逃跑。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据陈志强介绍：被强拆前，当地镇政府和办事处的人曾和他们谈过拆迁问题，他们家有产权房</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多平米，没有产权的房屋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>多平米，但仅给他们赔偿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多万，因此没有达成协议，不久就发生上述深夜强拆事件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PiYQdOB_oFk/UgJDOYYoOZI/AAAAAAAAmcc/LNnNl7Pbh5g/s1600/IMG_0359.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-PiYQdOB_oFk/UgJDOYYoOZI/AAAAAAAAmcc/LNnNl7Pbh5g/s320/IMG_0359.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CWmA6zwoE9c/UgJDOBGFv0I/AAAAAAAAmcQ/S1Wdc3_3uLo/s1600/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+IMG_20130619_080456.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CWmA6zwoE9c/UgJDOBGFv0I/AAAAAAAAmcQ/S1Wdc3_3uLo/s320/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+IMG_20130619_080456.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZtNdWJTFCXU/UgJDOEPdL3I/AAAAAAAAmcM/VhLKplpe6oY/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ZtNdWJTFCXU/UgJDOEPdL3I/AAAAAAAAmcM/VhLKplpe6oY/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+002.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VrdgoU8Z-K0/UgJDRiTtrjI/AAAAAAAAmck/uarrjBpI6zE/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+032.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-VrdgoU8Z-K0/UgJDRiTtrjI/AAAAAAAAmck/uarrjBpI6zE/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+032.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}